Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.14,0:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.28,0:00:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.66,0:00:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.27,0:00:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.45,0:00:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.39,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.89,0:01:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.94,0:01:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去洗手間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要追嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 先等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗手間內的牆壁和地板全部貼有瓷磚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窗戶無法開啟外側還有鋁制的格子窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然她很輕易就能打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 她應該不會幹這麼粗暴的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#11 草迷宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去吧 買給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.79,0:02:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啤酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能用體內反應器分解酒精的人真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 這次新人錄用測驗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難易度設定會不會搞錯了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說傻話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種程度都無法突破的話就表示訓練生的素質太差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣說也沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊喝咖啡一邊看報紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是問你 我問的是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的就是他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全放鬆下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會被假記憶欺騙的念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們完全沒有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一點剛開始我就教過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的人數呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3組6名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我去下一組咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最後一組了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們失去目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼接下來打算怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想再搜尋一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不會太冷淡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同情他們有什麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯絡不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會生氣先回去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入侵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是入侵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有4層防壁被突破的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是訓練生干的那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏就是終點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼感覺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.47,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皮膚觸覺接受器收到的感覺是明確的現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是卻完全沒有現實感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義體嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可愛吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是這裏的店主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,類似吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想寄放什麼東西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寄放?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏做的生意是寄放客戶的外部記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這裏的東西全是外人看來沒什麼價值的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.24,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但每一件卻都裝滿著擁有者非常多的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我常常會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這些東西散發出來的殘留思念感動得喘不過氣來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘留思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.43,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不也是被那個吸引到這邊來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以全身義體來說算是非常早期製作的珍貴產品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩個孩子身上的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總讓我覺得很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.78,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在此同時我也品嚐到受托保管他人記憶的快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩個孩子之間有什麼樣的記憶呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.16,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 已經這麼晚了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉 今天我要提早關門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次有時間的時候請再度光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屆時我會慢慢把故事說給你聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個奇妙的感覺是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鄉愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天再跟少校報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要就這樣不見人影嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次錄用有幾個可能過關的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長的朋友推薦進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前陸自情報部出身的男子1名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人不放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,素質下降雖然是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 確保有預備人員的確也是當務之急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是難易度設定如果再降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會搞得外強中乾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改天追加測試嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟課長討論過再決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得我適合當訓練教官嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.96,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要是不適合的話就沒人適合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是來9課之前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5分鐘就會被少校甩掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水準還真低啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼要是老大你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.58,0:11:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對少校這種突然消失的目標有辦法跟蹤到最後嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白日夢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是更靈異的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.13,0:11:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我曾在翻身的時候靈魂出竅看到奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有在自己的東西上面感受到思念過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長距離開車當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有過車子本身好像手腳延長的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在叫小包過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得好好玩一次好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我有件非做不可的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來逛昨天的路線做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現我在跟蹤她了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你差不多該到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.07,0:13:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這兩個孩子已經等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就快點告訴我這兩個孩子的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是急性子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩具義體以前一直都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.02,0:13:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由長大之後的男孩小心保管著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩在6歲的時候遇到飛機事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說是大多數乘客都罹難的嚴重事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被救出來的人也都在短時間內過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.21,0:13:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這個男孩和恰巧坐在他旁邊的女孩還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然兩人奇跡似的撿回一條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是女孩沒有恢復意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩除了左手之外全身完全無法活動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體上的傷恢復之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩很快就明白了自己的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是一起搭機的父母雙雙死亡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是遠房親戚剛開始很親切地來看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻馬上疏遠他的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他都用那小小的腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很努力的去接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.56,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後他把睡在隔壁床跟自己有著同樣遭遇的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看作是這世界上唯一的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望她能夠醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.64,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一邊這樣祈禱邊用一隻左手拚命折紙鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩出事了 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久之後女孩的病情急速惡化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血壓60
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有舒張壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注射各一單位的抗心律不整藥和強心劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ECF(細胞外液)不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血壓降到40
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上準備手術室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.28,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩聽說女孩到很遠的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又過了兩年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩不跟任何人說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是默默的折著紙鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿繼續折那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是上天賦予他的人生重責大任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天說了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說要白色的折紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訴訟等手續全部結束的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個年輕醫生和某個男性親戚來到醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟男孩這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你願意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有種治療法可以換掉你所有不能動的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問他有沒有嘗試的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說如果順利就可以像以前那樣正常生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩沒有回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是男孩提不起勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有想要回到以前那種正常生活的動機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了繼續折紙鶴外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已經對任何事情都沒有興趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此周圍的大人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都放棄說服男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.06,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 有個女孩卻創造了開啟男孩心扉的契機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是這孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.97,0:17:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子已經接受全身義體治療並且獲得成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是那個年輕醫生 認為這是說服男孩的最後手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才將兩個人拉在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩每天都來看男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是個非常開朗活潑的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.49,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,習慣全身義體之前應該很難熬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.43,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她卻從沒跟男孩訴苦過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但如此 她還一有機會就勸男孩做義體化手術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然男孩一直默默聽著不說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天卻突然這樣對她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「你能用義體折紙鶴嗎?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「如果做得到 要我全身義體化也行」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.66,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她雖然能夠用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻還沒有辦法控制義體做出細緻的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子大概是不認輸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想盡辦法拚命折著紙鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對男孩來說那個女孩應該是一種希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.61,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 兩個人都還太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩很失望地說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.81,0:19:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不能為死去的女孩折紙鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「那我維持現狀就好」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那天開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩在男孩面前消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只留下一句 「這次換我為你練習折紙鶴了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就是男孩一直以為已經死去的那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼她不說出這件事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許有什麼重大的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩從那天起就決定自己也要義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且在心裏發誓要去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從醫院消失的那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來男孩也全身義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熬過艱苦的復健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.07,0:20:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長大成為優秀的義體使用者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.61,0:20:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還是個很少有兒童換全身義體的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是超乎想像的艱苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是一想到那個女孩也承受過同樣的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就能很輕易的熬過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他找到那個女孩了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛機事故後換成全身義體的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的線索應該已經足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但就是找不到那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這女孩的義體是在哪裏找到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.91,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩在大學實驗室的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到這個被當成標本保存下來的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.88,0:21:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩雖然一眼就知道她就是自己尋找的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.39,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是到最後還是找不到更換義體SIZE的女孩本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以女孩這方面的記憶到現在還是空白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男孩現在人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大戰後期出兵到外國就斷了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.51,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來就再也沒來過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你告訴我這些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也一定還在尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次喜歡上的男孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次喜歡上的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰紅茶的冰塊快溶光了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說關於那些傢伙的測驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在重新考慮難易度設定的條件下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.33,0:22:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓他們再測驗一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.64,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是吹什麼風啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得我剛進游擊隊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也曾經意外的無法發揮實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挨長官一頓臭罵啊
